## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **API Keys and Local vs. Cloud Embeddings**
> We support two embedding providers:
> 1.  **Local (`sentence-transformers` using `"all-MiniLM-L6-v2"`)**: Free, runs offline, runs on CPU/GPU locally. Great for local development and testing.
> 2.  **Cloud (`google-generativeai` using `"models/embedding-001"`)**: High-quality Gemini embeddings. Requires internet access and a valid `GEMINI_API_KEY` set in your `.env` file.
> 
> By default, the system will look for a `GEMINI_API_KEY`. If not found, it will automatically fall back to the local embedding model to ensure the code works out-of-the-box.

