### 5. Vector Storage Layer

#### [NEW] [chroma_store.py](file:///c:/Users/suvan/Desktop/AI%20+%20LLM%20+%20RAG/agentic-ai/src/vector_store/chroma_store.py)
*   Define `BaseVectorStore(ABC)` interface:
    *   `add_chunks(chunks: List[DocumentChunk], embeddings: List[List[float]]) -> None`
    *   `delete_document_chunks(sha256: str) -> None`
    *   `similarity_search(query_vector: List[float], limit: int = 3) -> List[DocumentChunk]`
*   Implement `ChromaVectorStore` wrapping `chromadb.PersistentClient`.
*   Implement the **idempotency rule**: when adding chunks, first trigger `delete_document_chunks(sha256)` to wipe out stale chunks of the same file, avoiding duplicates.

